objects.description: [FIN6](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0037) has used a Metasploit PowerShell module to download and execute shellcode and to set up a local listener. [FIN6](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0037) has also used scripting to iterate through a list of compromised PoS systems, copy data to a log file, and remove the original data files.

external_references.description: FireEye Threat Intelligence. (2016, April). Follow the Money: Dissecting the Operations of the Cyber Crime Group FIN6. Retrieved June 1, 2016.
